    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p>The Engine represents evolution, innovation and creation. It flows with the manufacture of all things new and all things plentiful. A sound in perfect harmony that is best unceasing. The Engine's Growth represents innovation over nature.</p><p><strong>Constellation </strong>@UUID[Compendium.immortal-ardor.deities.Item.nErOKPlLvcxcp31v]{The Engine}</p><hr /><p><strong>First Asterism </strong>(Level 5): You gain the @UUID[Compendium.immortal-ardor.spells.Item.y3m3dsIGeT0JoIN2]{Engine's Growth} constellation spell. You also gain a +1 status bonus to Reflex saving throws.</p><p><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:initial;scrollbar-color:initial\">Second Asterism </strong>(Level 9): You can cast this spell or any other Second Asterism Nebula Facet spell an additional time in a day. The bonus increases to +2.</span></p><p><strong>Third Asterism</strong> (Level 17): You can cast this spell or any other Third Asterism Nebula Facet spell an additional time in a day. The bonus increases to +3.</p>"
